      "content": "i dont know... it feels like you're just saying that to be nice. honestly, it feels like the opposite. it feels like i'm just a placeholder. if a lightbulb in an office building burns out, nobody stops to mourn the light, they just replace it or leave it dark. that's how i feel. like, if i just quietly disappeared, it wouldn't even be a tragedy. it would just be... less noise. wouldn't it just be easier for everyone if things were just quieter?",
